00:20:08.259 --> 00:20:12.259
It all came out, so we had lots of elders meetings.

00:20:12.259 --> 00:20:19.259
So I really made an effort to try to have a relationship myself with Jehovah.

00:20:19.259 --> 00:20:25.259
Oh, telling my parents was harder than anything.

00:20:25.259 --> 00:20:28.259
Because when you're involved in wrongdoing,

00:20:28.259 --> 00:20:30.259
you think, this is me I'm hurting.

00:20:30.259 --> 00:20:33.259
I know I'm hurting myself, but I decide to hurt myself.

00:20:33.259 --> 00:20:35.259
And it doesn't affect anybody else.

