What I regret most is that I wasted all these years

00:21:19.779 --> 00:21:24.779
being selfish when I could have been serving Jehovah.

00:21:24.779 --> 00:21:28.779
My parents, they really had a lot of love for me,

00:21:28.779 --> 00:21:31.779
but I don't know.

00:21:31.779 --> 00:21:35.779
In return, I just gave them basically nothing but heartache.

00:21:35.779 --> 00:21:39.779
